  "title": "Senior Retail Manager",
  "description": "<h5>Responsibilities</h5>\n<p>In-charge of overall store day-to-day operations and ensure smooth operations</p>\n<p>Develop and implement sales strategies aimed at consistently driving sales volume and achieving store sales targets.</p>\n<p>Lead and supervise the retail team members to ensure they achieve desired outcomes and effectively address any employee concerns.</p>\n<p>Responsibly handle and address customer inquiries regarding product, pricing, availability, delivery or any other related matters.</p>\n<p>Assist in store promotional events and campaigns with the corporate team.</p>\n<p>Roster planning.</p>\n<p>Ad hoc duties as assigned.</p>\n<p>Requirements</p>\n<p>Diploma in any discipline</p>\n<p>At least 3 - 5 years of relevant working experience in fashion retail industry preferrably with supervisory experience</p>\n<p>Good communication and presentation skills</p>",
